---
title: Kale and Quinoa Power-Up Salad with Toasted Almonds
description: Quinoa kale salad: three words that never fail to capture our attention. This dish isn’t just loaded with the good stuff, it also has plenty of other delicious toppings that make it impossible to resist: a honey Dijon dressing, cranberries, almonds, and feta cheese. In other words, it’s pure and powerful awesomeness in a bowl.
